So good! If you get the chance, the restaurant is just on the other side of the bridge and is a great experience. Amazing food, good portions, reasonable prices, great ambience, super attentive staff. Went to one of their dinner series at end of September and it was phenomenal. Looks like we missed on the Cuba dinner series (10/23), but coming up is Korea (11/6) and Thailand (11/20). <http://lechonpdx.com/>
